description: The OMICS group at PNNL has developed a wide range of software utilities over the last 15+ years. These tools are used to manage data files, transform data, visualize data, and automate data processing. The software is distributed on GitHub as open source, typically under the Apache 2.0 license agreement. See https://github.com/PNNL-Comp-Mass-Spec Lipid analysis tool developed by PNNL
name: PNNL-Comp-Mass-Spec/LIQUID
